ude but at somewhat lower distance (redshift) than the\ngravitational transition recently proposed to address the Hubble and growth\ntensions ($\\frac{\\Delta G}{G}\\simeq -0.1$ at transition redshift $z_t\\lesssim\n0.01$ ($D_c\\lesssim 40 Mpc$)).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Apr 2021 16:45:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 11 Jul 2021 06:22:30 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 7 Oct 2021 14:31:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-08"}
