 its initial temperature. The shocks generate\nthe jets with a quasi-periodical behavior that follows a parabolic path on\ntime-distance plots consistent with macrospicule jets' observed dynamics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Apr 2021 18:46:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-12"}
