upling\nlimit. We propose feasible methods for detecting the characteristic time-scales\nthat could be observable by the Andreev spectroscopy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Apr 2021 11:31:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-03"}
