, both renewable deployment and emission allowance auctioning are\neffectively reducing GHG emissions and promoting low-carbon economic path.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Apr 2021 15:31:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-03"}
